---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'ContactPage',
  name: 'Book a Personal Chef',
  mainEntity: { '@type': 'LocalBusiness', name: 'Olympic Peninsula Personal Chef' }
};
---
<BaseLayout title="Book a Personal Chef | Port Angeles, Sequim & Olympic Peninsula" description="Request a custom proposal for private dining, meal prep, and vacation rental chef services in Port Angeles, Sequim, and across the Olympic Peninsula." path="/contact" schema={schema}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container local-grid">
      <div class="card-stack">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Inquire about your date</p>
          <h1>Tell us what you’re planning, and we’ll shape the right chef experience around it.</h1>
          <p>Whether you need a private dinner in Port Angeles, recurring meal prep in Sequim, or a chef-led vacation rental experience on the Olympic Peninsula, your inquiry begins a calm, personalized proposal process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card schema-note">
          <p><strong>What happens next:</strong> You’ll receive a thoughtful response with service recommendations, menu direction, and pricing guidance based on your guest count, timeline, and location.</p>
          <p><strong>Dietary accommodations:</strong> Allergies, gluten-free, pescatarian, dairy-free, wellness-focused, and family-specific preferences are all welcome.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-strip">
          <div><strong>Fast follow-up</strong><span>Most inquiries receive a reply within one business day.</span></div>
          <div><strong>Custom proposals</strong><span>Menus and logistics are built for your actual occasion, not from a fixed package list.</span></div>
          <div><strong>Premium, approachable service</strong><span>Expect polished hospitality that feels warm, discreet, and easy to work with.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <form class="card form-grid" name="booking" method="post" action="#">
        <label>Name<input type="text" name="name" autocomplete="name" required /></label>
        <label>Email<input type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required /></label>
        <label>Phone<input type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" /></label>
        <label>Event Type
          <select name="eventType">
            <option>Weekly Meal Prep</option>
            <option>Private Dinner</option>
            <option>Vacation Rental Chef Experience</option>
            <option>Small Event Catering</option>
            <option>Holiday Meal</option>
            <option>Custom Dietary Plan</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label>Guest Count<input type="number" name="guestCount" min="1" /></label>
        <label>Preferred Date<input type="date" name="date" /></label>
        <label>Location<input type="text" name="location" placeholder="Port Angeles, Sequim, or your Olympic Peninsula property" /></label>
        <label>Dietary Needs<input type="text" name="dietaryNeeds" placeholder="Allergies, preferences, wellness goals, children's needs" /></label>
        <label class="full-span">Message<textarea name="message" placeholder="Share the occasion, menu style you have in mind, desired level of service, and any details that will help us create a thoughtful proposal."></textarea></label>
        <div class="full-span form-note">
          <p>There is no pressure to have every detail finalized. A strong starting point is enough for us to recommend the best service format and next steps.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="full-span"><button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request Your Proposal</button></div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
